              <div class="mb-8 flex w-fit mx-auto p-5 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">Residential Plumbing</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8">Full-service home plumbing. Repairs, upgrades, and peace of mind for local homeowners.</p>
              <button type="button" onclick="scrollToBookOnline('Residential')" class="flex items-center space-x-2 font-black text-blue-600 group-hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors justify-center md:justify-start">
                <span>Book Residential Service</span>
